title: State Minimum Wage Rate for Georgia
notes:
This series has been disaggregated from annual frequency into monthly by interpolating the annual values and repeating those values for every month in the year. This series is only experimental and should be used with caution. 

State minimum wage applies only when a certain number of workers are employed.

For more information, visit https://www.dol.gov/whd/state/stateMinWageHis.htm
